"Hear that sound, Roger?

149
00:09:06,278 --> 00:09:09,981
That's the sound
of newspapers being printed."

150
00:09:09,982 --> 00:09:14,085
<i>Unlike in movies,
you didn't stop the presses.</i>

151
00:09:14,086 --> 00:09:18,756
